The applied discounts can coexist and can be differentiated into the following types:

* Customers
	* With trade attributes linked to customer master data and sales document header

* Items
	* By value, percentage or with basket gifts
	* in base of tresholds (by min or max value)
	* With trade attributes linked to item master data and sales document line

* Documents
	* By value, percentage or with basket gifts
	* In compliance with filters on item assortments, type and threshold value of document and/or single reference
	* With trade attributes linked to item and sales document line


